text: Nicolae Cristea (born 11 October 1942) is a Romanian wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle 57 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:Living people Category:Romanian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Romania Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
